    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 10</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>A lesser variant of Usagido, this seal is designed to conceal and contain part of a creature's strength. The target suffers a -1 penalty to Strength and Speed Ranks, Defense and weapon damage, and its maximum Chakra Pool is reduced by 5. The seal can be dispelled by its bearer by concentrating for a move action.</p>\n\n\n\n",
